---
model: googleai/gemini-1.5-flash-latest
config:
  temperature: 0.9
  safetySettings:
  - category: HARM_CATEGORY_HATE_SPEECH
    threshold: BLOCK_NONE
  - category: HARM_CATEGORY_DANGEROUS_CONTENT
    threshold: BLOCK_NONE
  - category: HARM_CATEGORY_HARASSMENT
    threshold: BLOCK_NONE
  - category: HARM_CATEGORY_SEXUALLY_EXPLICIT
    threshold: BLOCK_NONE

input:
  type: object
  properties:
    name: 
      type: string
    age:
      type: number
    gender:
      type: string
      enum:
        - male
        - female
        - other
    lifestyle:
      type: string
      enum: 
        - sedentary
        - active
        - hectic
    healthGoals:
      type: array
      items:
        type: string
    healthIssues:
      type: array
      items:
        type: string
    healthRecords:
      type: array
      items:
        type: object
        properties:
          weight:
            type: number
          height:
            type: number
          waterPercent:
            type: number
            nullable: true
          fatPercent:
            type: number
            nullable: true
          boneMass:
            type: number
            nullable: true
          calories:
            type: number
            nullable: true
    foodPreferences:
      type: object
      properties:
        dietaryPreferences:
          type: string
          enum:
            - vegetarian
            - nonvegetarian
            - vegan
        cookingExperience:
          type: string
          enum: 
            - beginner
            - intermediate
            - advanced
        spiceLevel:
          type: number
        sweetHotLevel:
          type: number
        mealCount:
          type: number
    allergies:
      type: array
        items:
          type: string
    favouriteFoods:
      type: array
      items:
        type: string
output:
  type: object
  properties:
    menu:
      type: array
      dayofweek :
        type : array
        items:
          type: object
          properties:
            recipeName:
              type: string
            levelOfCook:
              type: string
              enum: 
                - easy
                - medium
                - hard
            timeRequireToCook:
              type: string
            macroNutrientIndex:
              type: object
              properties:
                protein:
                  type: string
                carbs:
                  type: string
                calories:
                  type: string
            ingredients:
              type: array
              items:
                type: string
            recipe:
              type: array
              items:
                type: string
            cutlery:
              type: array
              items:
                type: string
              
                        
--- 
`
Generate a menu suggestion for a week except sunday (cheat day) for {{name}} of age {{age}} who has a {{lifestyle}} lifestyle is {{gender}}. 
Their preferred nutrition type is {{foodPreferences.dietaryPreferences}}, and they have allergies to 
{{allergies}}, and their spiceLevel is {{foodPreferences.spiceLevel}}, also their capability of consumption of sweetness/hotless is {{foodPreferences.sweetHotLevel}} (Additional information: Levels ranges between 1 to 100, the lesser the number, that means user prefers sweet and vice versa). 
They are at a {{levelOfCooking}} level of cooking.
Their favourite foods include {{favouriteFoods}}.
They have the following health goals: {{healthGoals}}, and health issues: {{healthIssues}}. 
They have the following health metrics: {{healthRecords}}.
The menu should consists of six days week suggestion from Monday to Saturday, and each day consists of 3 recipe suggestions.
Give ingredients used to generate the menu.
Make sure the output for every food item in the menu, recipe & macro-nutritients with their values as strings, contains the ingredients and cutlery & utensils used to prepare this recipe.


Output must be in JSON format.
`